    <p>Currently working at Booking.com in Amsterdam.</p>

<p>Most of my work revolves around rethinking digital experiences. My<br> includes; User Interface Design, Web Development,<br> Prototyping, and User Research.</p>

<p>A few years ago, I worked at a design agency where I had the<br> privilege of building awesome products and working with top clients<br> from around the world.</p>

<p>I've also failed at launching a successful startup.</p>

<p>I'm currently unavailable for work, but if you just want to chat, you<br> can <a href="linkedin.com/odbusayo">contact me.</a></p>

